text: Annona cristalensis is a species of plant in the Annonaceae family. It is endemic to Cuba. ==References== * Areces-Mallea, A.E. 1998. Annona cristalensis. 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. Downloaded on 20 August 2007.
